    "description": "• K A L P A V R I K S H A •\n\nMaster Bedroom \n\nFirst attempt at bringing traditional design colors to life-bold, vibrant, and daring to break the mold. Exploring fresh possibilities while honoring timeless root.\n\nEvery project has a story, but some resonate deeper. This home, designed for an Air Officer who has lived with his family across the length and breadth of India, carries with it the spirit of journeys, traditions, and belonging. What made the process truly special was the enthusiasm and involvement of the family-matching our passion at every stage of design and execution. From site work to craftsmanship, each step reflects not just a physical build but a weaving together of memories, cultures, and values into a timeless, traditional home. Architecture, at its finest, is never only about walls and spaces—it’s about creating a place for life’s stories to unfold with grace and warmth✨\n\nProject : Kalpavriksha\nDesign by : @hastayu_  @laxmi_uppin \n📍Dharwad\n\n📸 @the_view_finderr \n\n#traditionalarchitecture #masterbedroom #traditionalinterior #antique #posterbed",
